{"tid":1201110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(長文)抗爭過來人經驗分享","createTime":"2019-06-11T02:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T17:47:21.000Z","uid":57076,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad48af9240d0f1e84419cdea4188b852b0fff48","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:41:25.000Z","msg":"小弟2012到2019年，就算係前線，都未比人拉過，可以分享下小小經驗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">物資準備</span><br />\n-水<br />\n-口罩2-3個<br />\n-帽<br />\n-護眼罩(建議帶3M)<br />\n-安全帽<br />\n-備用衣服(盡量著純色衫，長䄂)<br />\n-風樓<br />\n-雨傘<br />\n-電筒(萬一就比人捉到，開電筒照然後逃生)<br />\n-尿袋充電線<br />\n-索帶<br />\n其他好多都非必要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">地理位置:</span><br />\n想留守特定要地，一定要先觀察好附近地理位置，最好就有朋友結伴同行<br />\n<br />\n最少二個燈塔，負責觀察二個不同方向的派兵調動(主要從灣仔總部調出)<br />\n<br />\n警察無論係佈防同兵力都強化左唔少，反而市民入面80%都係16-25歲，好多缺乏經驗，所以避免正面接觸<br />\n<br />\n最緊要睇市民人數，如果少過1000以下，警察就開始聚集<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">大原則:</span><br />\n不受傷<br />\n不被捕<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">具體內容</span><br />\n-首先要認清人群，如果見到可疑係警察，可以先chok佢，好多時警察會怕，或者表明身份<br />\n<br />\n-由於對方有長盾同棍，盡量保持遠距離，可以帶備電筒照明<br />\n<br />\n-如果遇到圍捕，一定要走去大路，唔好走小路，因為好容易比人暗角打<br />\n<br />\n-百花齊放，分散小隊，但人數維持十數人以上<br />\n<br />\n-萬一遇上危險，雙手護頭，咪雙手舉起投降咁款，因為都會照打你<br />\n<br />\n-臨被圍捕關頭，必要時開電筒<br />\n<br />\n-可以移師到領事館，美國/德國等，警察係領事館沒有執法權<br />\n<br />\n-可以係telegram 搜尋@policeHK_bot，現場表揚香港警察，呼叫警察姓名<br />\n<br />\n-有鏡頭可以影住對方<br />\n<br />\n-嘗試找紙皮，或者強化雨傘，可擋胡椒噴霧及警棍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-如果有自己人比警察拉走，一定，一定要拉翻翻嚟，同時要小心有警察幫拖<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">手機通訊方面:</span><br />\n1.建議用telegram,尤其係secret chat,有end-to-end cryption<br />\n<br />\n2.定期清理手機訊息<br />\n<br />\n3.千祈唔好係任何公海講任何行動訊息，大量警察mon post<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔好向陌生人透露電話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n5.如果需要到前線，先將中英文全名同身份證交比唔會上前線的朋友，一旦被捕，可以致電伍展邦律師行電話26081400</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時咁多，有需要再補充"},{"pid":"8c0a5fa4d8ba3e696acd0be591cb11c737dbad39","tid":1201110,"uid":70201,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"Strong post push<br />\n<br />\n唔好氣餒! 有圖為證! 嗰日遊行其實已經唔止103萬人! 大家一齊撐埋呢兩日!<br />\n[非專業] 我想知我統計學有冇警察咁差<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4e05126f232113d4e45a16793526f36f751bc1b","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"物資要分散多人拎，派比前線，唔好一次比人充公晒"},{"pid":"fda2b4786455c4911e92e5d052ac01a3ef4d2552","tid":1201110,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"人手置頂"},{"pid":"62e165b2a9b11edc0392084bce9c9bcb233b3ef3","tid":1201110,"uid":166794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"1.建議用telegram,尤其係secret chat,有end-to-end <span style=\"color: red;\">en</span>cryption"},{"pid":"f6d4f4b8172c3bc87fd2e8e089110958b7056ecb","tid":1201110,"uid":166794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4154842f6bc3fc58dafdf59e25ef86596fed64ea","tid":1201110,"uid":96300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:47:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"dc1abaa30c8cf916d31c7c1d704d2b5212cd4c7d","tid":1201110,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"好有用"},{"pid":"518240ab71c7aa393e94b39c6d25a12383507a76","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"電筒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecpkKxu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecpkKxu.jpg&h=70d771ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好長小小"},{"pid":"05483b9c40892277a2d717cd3dea2d59b4700878","tid":1201110,"uid":206421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"165d8e74b6049c4f18bc0ebea7fec5ec612bc709","tid":1201110,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:53:45.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3c9ab86c2056f65bd7df64067bb2ab6465cec225","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YDqLVF1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDqLVF1.jpg&h=928fe2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長傘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81c9f8ae0560d2906143d0c79aced98dab7424a","tid":1201110,"uid":181111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43148d3ca69247341dc473b4439f0a44c9a9be71","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"要上前線就唔好跟大隊著白衫，<br />\n<br />\n衣服以black bloc為主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNUAytR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNUAytR.jpg&h=2afcf5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次警察有去灣仔，中環等等地方查白衫市民身份證，甚至到旺角拉人<br />\n<br />\n轉載<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrAzO28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrAzO28.jpg&h=be87e151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家如果搭小巴出旺角，記住提早落車，然後轉車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果幾個都識既，可以搭的士，轉最少2程"},{"pid":"544574ea81e5d3a32c2627f98327e537fddf850d","tid":1201110,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3a5d8f1b9a980829e5cd3964b47854ade806fa29","tid":1201110,"uid":181624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2f3702d9fdf1977632e0886a86cc3f20c0ab3daf","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"如果被捕，老西都唔好講任何野，呢個時候係心理戰，意志要強大，唔夠證據都係坐臭格就會放翻出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好開手機，唔好賣隊友</span><br />\n有時警察會話你朋友xx已經認罪或者透露資訊，事實上只係試你地，戰友們一定要互相信任，不篤灰"},{"pid":"e4b0d13d2fed84124f6ead1d0df77a30cb73e4e9","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:16:24.000Z","msg":"[現場人士工具]一秒令警員冷靜執法既工具<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1196620\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1196620</a>"},{"pid":"2fe0be12765b52f16252fece514a161b50c9c941","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:18:31.000Z","msg":"［好撚重要，廣傳］多圖抗爭手冊（裝備list）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1197512\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1197512</a>"},{"pid":"e12a7ddbe69b1363b8479cb92b4cb1b0d2deebee","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPQW2xh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPQW2xh.jpg&h=b0bb912d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手套"},{"pid":"849debdbd513321fa37915f42701c5d1a9c00522","tid":1201110,"uid":218994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"認真 <br />\n護陰"},{"pid":"6d2bd39be5b050314d85230356bee9caea6ad1e6","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"849debdbd513321fa37915f42701c5d1a9c00522","tid":1201110,"uid":218994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"認真 <br />\n護陰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"我都醒起，單車褲加厚pad"},{"pid":"2da37387419d9148b5bf7b7798700f7aab20aaac","tid":1201110,"uid":129139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efa16d8c70029caebf7508d7ece8e355a34038f5","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31be44d420c76f83e0d172bb1dd6191d05e80edf","tid":1201110,"uid":57076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"停用大陸apps<br />\n-微信<br />\n-淘寶<br />\n-支付寶<br />\n-百度地圖<br />\n等等<br />\n防止被中國locate到"}]}